Package com.abmash.api.data

Provides data classes in a browser context.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Date Date class to extract dates from web pages.
List Represents a list on a webpage, use it by calling Browser#getList(String)) or Browser.getList(HtmlElement).
Table Represents a table on a webpage, use it by calling Browser#getTable(String)) or Browser.getTable(HtmlElement).
TableRow Represents a row in a Table.
TableRows  
 

Package com.abmash.api.data Description

Provides data classes in a browser context.

Date extracts a date from an HtmlElement by using the HtmlElement.extractDate() method.

Table and TableRow are used to represent tables

List is used to represent lists
